high_descs: Turn right and walk to the stove then turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the green cup to the right of the toaster.
Turn right and walk to the sink and then turn left to face it.
Wash the cup in the sink and make sure to close the faucet when you're done.
Turn right and walk until you're even with the microwave on your right then turn right and walk to it.
Put the green cup under the mug to the microwaves left side.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean mug on the table.

high_descs: Turn to the right and head towards the toaster on the counter.
Pick up the green cup on the counter.
Head right towards the sink with the cup.
Clean the cup with water in the sink.
Take the cup and turn around and bring it to the table with the microwave on it.
Put the cup next to the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned green cup next to the microwave.

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk across the room, then turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the green cup on the counter.
Turn to the right and take one step forward then turn to the left to face the sink.
Put the green glass in the sink and turn on the faucet, then fill up the sink before turning the water off and taking the glass out.
Turn to the right and take two steps then turn to the right and walk across the room.
Place the green glass on the counter to the left of the microwave.
